{"tid":1777613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和你非專場-和你樹聖誕活動","createTime":"2019-12-10T10:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T10:51:23.000Z","uid":5281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6731dc223dab0d0e4089368dda5f6cdbfbf26fa7","tid":1777613,"uid":5281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"今年聖誕節區區冇曬聖誕氣氛，不如每人帶一棵聖誕樹去商場中庭位置之後進行活動好冇？<br />\n<br />\n冇野要衝擊！只係返自己區一齊慶祝！一齊大聲唱！唱到比所有手足都聽到！they are not alone!!!<br />\n<br />\n有人扮聖誕老人就最好！<br />\n時間:不限<br />\n<br />\n物資<br />\n1.聖誕樹（可以利用廢紙自制，唔建議用新鮮樹）<br />\n2.裝飾品 （Usb燈飾等等)<br />\n3.memo<br />\n4.聖誕文宣<br />\n5.交換禮物比手足（衣服等等）做到既話<br />\n<br />\n活動內容<br />\n1.唱聖誕歌<br />\n2.唱聖詩（我唔係耶撚，傳統黎）<br />\n3.唱榮光<br />\n4.<br />\n5.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論！可以的話直接喺區TG內討論"},{"pid":"524e5fac04d3bdce263f75b1a5208d139ca96f02","tid":1777613,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"和你樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜鳩名黎"},{"pid":"701d49acd4fc204bbd61c96e6b0bca1dc2e986ed","tid":1777613,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"524e5fac04d3bdce263f75b1a5208d139ca96f02","tid":1777613,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"和你樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜鳩名黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"係都和你飾/和你裝飾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa